channel.title: Mod idea will make ausom sink so much easyer
channel.description: I know I have been posting a lot presently but that its because I have mod ideas, bug's I have found, and general questions. I am in a ticket race with my brother in the ausom sink and we are allowed to use mods. But there is one mod that I found but was outdated the Ausom points X100 ( mod link https://ficsit.app/mod/CTbhnCnW8zWWGG ) and I was wondering if someone could make a mod like this and or reach out to the mod dev and update it if allowed and I want to make my own mods so I don't have to post these stupid forums all the time about mod ideas but I don't know how yet I am trying to find a non-gibrish guide( i can't find one that makes any sense)
